Description: LingmoOS AI Assistant - multi-backend AI chat client
 LingmoOS AI Assistant is a Material Design 3 chat client supporting multiple
 AI backends: DeepSeek, Ollama (local and cloud), and llama.cpp for local GGUF
 models.
 .
 It features streaming responses, conversation history management with
 token-budget-based context trimming, hardware-aware model parameter
 selection, and custom fonts (Outfit, Noto Sans SC, JetBrains Mono).
 .
 Built with Qt6 and QML on Debian.
